components.activityColumnRef:
CASE 
   WHEN <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 0 THEN
   "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"
  
   WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('6','8','9','A','T')) >= 1 AND  <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Electronic Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('7')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Mail Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('1')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Print Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"
         
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('2','4')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Print Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"
         
         
         
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order Update' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('6','8','9','A','T')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Electronic Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order Update' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('7')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Mail Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
        
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order Update' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('1')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Print Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"
        
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Purchase Order Update' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('2','4')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Electronic Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    
    
    
    WHEN
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Dun Order Confirmation' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('6','8','9','A','T')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Electronic Message:  ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"

    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Dun Order Confirmation' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('7')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Mail Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
        
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Dun Order Confirmation' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('1')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Print Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Dun Order Confirmation' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('2','4')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Fax/ Telex Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
        
    
    
    
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Overdue Notice' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('6','8','9','A','T')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Electronic Message:  ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Overdue Notice' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('7')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Mail Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Overdue Notice' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('1')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Print Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    WHEN 
        "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = 'Send Overdue Notice' AND PU_COUNT("EKKO","NAST"."NACHA","NAST"."NACHA" IN ('2','4')) >= 1 AND <%= process_explorer_classification %> = 1
    THEN 'Fax/ Telex Message: ' || "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" 
    
    
    
    
    ELSE "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"
END

activityConfigurations.name: Electronic Message: Send Purchase Order Update

components.title: #{ProcessExplorer}

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."NACHA" ) = 0 THEN 'No order message' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."OBJKY" , "NAST"."NACHA" IN ( '6' , '9' , 'A' ) ) >= 1 AND ISNULL ( "NAST"."DATVR" ) = 0 THEN 'Electronic order message' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."OBJKY" , "NAST"."NACHA" IN ( '1' ) ) >= 1 AND ISNULL ( "NAST"."DATVR" ) = 0 THEN 'Print order message' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."OBJKY" , "NAST"."NACHA" IN ( '7' ) ) >= 1 AND ISNULL ( "NAST"."DATVR" ) = 0 THEN 'Mail order message' ELSE 'Other' END AS "#{OrderMessageType}" FORMAT "%"

meta.columnName: What is the processing status of Order Mesages?
meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_LAST ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."VSTAT" ) = '0' THEN 'Message not processed' WHEN PU_LAST ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."VSTAT" ) = '1' THEN 'Message processed successfully' WHEN PU_LAST ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."VSTAT" ) = '2' THEN 'Message processed incorrectly' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKKO" , "NAST"."VSTAT" ) ) = 1 THEN 'No Message' ELSE 'n.A.' END AS "What is the processing status of Order Mesages?"

variables.value: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1000 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.000€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1000 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 1.000 - 10.000€' ELSE 'e) > 10.000€' END
